 154:				;	... SUBROUTINE TO BUILD IMAGE OF FORMATTED TRACK ...
 155:				;
 156:				;	PARAMETERS ARE:  IX ....... (POINTER TO FORMAT PARAMETERS)
 157:				;			 IY ....... (TABLE OF SECTOR NUMBERS)
 158:				;			 TRKPTR ... (POINTER TO TRACK DATA BUFFER)
